Title: Chinar Daastaan-E-Ishq
Writer: Ahmed Chaudhary, Mohsin Khan (screenplay), Sahar Quaze (screen play and dialogue), Renzu Shah
Actors: Parveen Kaur, Faisal Khan, Shahbaaz Khan, Pramod Moutho
Plot: Based on Urdu novel Jheel Jalti Hai, the film aspires to be an iconic love story of Jamaal (Faissal Khan) and Suraiyya (Inayat Sharma). Sadly, more than the somber story, the experience of watching this film is more tragic.
